<p>Test connectivity with ICMP ping messages.</p>
<p>This runs over WireGuard; tell us which WireGuard tunnel to use by
running from within an app directory (with a &#39;fly.toml&#39;), passing the
&#39;-a&#39; flag with an app name, or the &#39;-o&#39; flag with an org name.</p>
<p>With no arguments, test connectivity to your gateway, the first hop
in our network, to see if your WireGuard connection is working.</p>
<p>The target argument can be either a &quot;.internal&quot; DNS name in our network
(the name of your application) or &quot;gateway&quot;.</p>
